snippet.title: MetroTD - Demo Launch Trailer | OUT NOW
snippet.description:
Demo Out now 
Search MetroTD in Steam
《MetroTD》 is a strategy tower defense survival Roguelike game. Design defensive lines, assemble battle carts and construct  firepower to destroy waves of enemies! Continuously experiment with different combinations of caravans and zones to slaughter the monsters.

Join the community: discord.gg/wQPB2Pdf
